_:N6b45dbe1e19b4120b1a472e01424f5da <http://schema.org/description> "The House of Commons is the publicly elected chamber of Parliament. Members of the Commons debate the big political issues of the day and proposals for new laws. Corporate Officers of the House of Commons is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Cabinet Office ." .
